T*
(- regular pseudo-session inter-arrival timing) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Rule contributions are separated into strong and supporting evidence. Strong) Tj
T*
(rules represent direct mechanical or replay-like patterns, such as impossible) Tj
T*
(timing or repeated query/domain behaviour. Supporting rules provide context,) Tj
T*
(such as volume, concentration, or broad clustering. Supporting contributions) Tj
T*
(are capped so several weak signals cannot add up to the same meaning as a) Tj
T*
(strong bot signal on their own.) Tj
